<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>My Docker Proxy - No Cache</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Docker Proxy for $VPS_HOST:$VPS_PORT</h1>
<p>此服务可做 HTTP/HTTPS 代理（CONNECT），不缓存镜像层。</p>

<ol>
    <li>在国内机器上设置环境变量：</li>
    <pre>export HTTP_PROXY="http://$VPS_HOST:$VPS_PORT"
export HTTPS_PROXY="http://$VPS_HOST:$VPS_PORT"
</pre>
    <li>或者编辑 <code>/etc/docker/daemon.json</code> 中：</li>
    <pre>{
  "proxies": {
    "httpProxy": "http://$VPS_HOST:$VPS_PORT",
    "httpsProxy": "http://$VPS_HOST:$VPS_PORT"
  }
}
</pre>
    <li>重启 Docker 并拉取镜像测试：</li>
    <pre>docker pull ubuntu:latest</pre>
</ol>
</body>
</html>
